Usage: Hyde [Function] [options]

 
[man]                       ï¬Œ Show Manual

 
[version]                   ï¬Œ Hyde-cli version

 
[systeminfo]                ï¬Œ System information

 
[check]                     ï¬Œ Information about Hyde and its components

			 [Config]  ï¬Œ [*] Hyde Config File & Directory status

						[--mismatch] ï¬Œ    Diff mismatched dotfiles
						[--preserve] ï¬Œ    Diff preserved dotfiles
						[--less] ï¬Œ    Pipes STDOUT to less

			 [Package]  ï¬Œ Hyde core Package status
 
[control]                   ï¬Œ Interactive control file

			 [Config]  ï¬Œ Manage users restore control list
 
[branch]                    ï¬Œ Set preavailable Hyde branch

 
[update]                    ï¬Œ Pull updates from Hyde repository

 
[upgrade]                   ï¬Œ Upgrades dots from the repository

 
[restore]                   ï¬Œ Restore dots

			 [Config]  ï¬Œ Only restores dots from default '/home/khing/.cache/hyde/Hyde-Clone/Configs'

			 [Clone]  ï¬Œ Restores dots from a clone repository 
  			                  ğŸ’¡ Provide ~/path/to/clone/directory

			 [BackUp]  ï¬Œ Restores dots from previous backup
  			                  !! Files might not be complete
  			                  ğŸ’¡ You can cherry pick a file/dir from a backup

			 [Link]  ï¬Œ Links a clone directory. Useful if you want to change your CloneDir
 
[backup]                    ï¬Œ Backing up commands

			 [all]  ï¬Œ Backs up the current configuration

			 [revert]  ï¬Œ Revert to a previous backup run by 'Hyde backup all'. 
  			                  ğŸ’¡ different from 'Hyde restore Backup', this command will restore the explicit backups like a snapshot

			 [list]  ï¬Œ List the backup

			 [clean]  ï¬Œ Clear some storage by deleting old backups
 
[override]                  ï¬Œ Overwrite current dots from the prefered user dir 
			 ğŸ’¡ see upstream for more info 
			 ğŸ’¡ add 'userPrefsDir=path/to/user/pref/directory' in
			'/home/khing/.config/hyde/hyde.conf' for custom user path

 
[cache]                     ï¬Œ Manages Hyde's cache

			 [reload]  ï¬Œ Reload wallpaper cache

			 [rebuild]  ï¬Œ Force rebuild cache
 
[cursor]                    ï¬Œ Cursor setting

			 [theme]  ï¬Œ Set cursor theme

			 [size]  ï¬Œ Set cursor size

			 [reload]  ï¬Œ Reload cursors

			 [info]  ï¬Œ Check active cursor status (only gsettings)
 
[theme]                     ï¬Œ Theme commands

			 [set]  ï¬Œ Set theme

			 [next]  ï¬Œ Next theme

			 [prev]  ï¬Œ Previous theme

			 [select]  ï¬Œ Theme selector

			 [patch]  ï¬Œ Patch a theme from different repository.
  			                 ğŸ’¡ Invoking without args will launch a menu from Hyde-gallery DB
 
[wallpaper]                 ï¬Œ Wallpaper commands

			 [set]  ï¬Œ Set /Path/to/Wallpapers as new wallpaper directory

			 [next]  ï¬Œ Next wallppaer

			 [prev]  ï¬Œ Previous wallpaper

			 [select]  ï¬Œ Wallpaper selector
 
[wallbash]                  ï¬Œ Toggle to use wallpaper accent themes

			 [toggle]  ï¬Œ Cycles wallbash [0] off [1] auto [2] dark [3] light

			 [mode]  ï¬Œ [*] Set wallbash mode. [0] [1] [2] [3] 
  			                 ğŸ’¡ no args spawns a menu

						[0] ï¬Œ  wallbash disabled
						[1] ï¬Œ  wallbash auto
						[2] ï¬Œ  wallbash dark mode
						[3] ï¬Œ  wallbash light mode
 
[waybar]                    ï¬Œ Waybar commands

			 [control]  ï¬Œ Edit waybar control file

			 [reload]  ï¬Œ Reloads waybar

			 [size]  ï¬Œ [*]Set waybar size

						[--all] ï¬Œ  Change all the pre-set sizes
 
[sddm]                      ï¬Œ Sddm commands

			 [theme]  ï¬Œ Select sddm theme
 
[shell]                     ï¬Œ Shell commands

			 [select]  ï¬Œ Shell selector
 
[power]                     ï¬Œ Power Options

			 [reset]  ï¬Œ Reset changes

			 [save]  ï¬Œ [*] Save power by disabling features

						[--animations] ï¬Œ  Disable animations
						[--borderangle] ï¬Œ  Disable border angle animation
						[--blur] ï¬Œ  Disable blur
						[--opacity] ï¬Œ  Disable tranparency

			 [toggle]  ï¬Œ Toggle ğŸ’¡ Set/unset current changes'

			 [unset]  ï¬Œ [*] Unset specific changes

						[--animations] ï¬Œ  Default animations
						[--borderangle] ï¬Œ  Default border angle animation
						[--blur] ï¬Œ  Default blur
						[--opacity] ï¬Œ  Default tranparency

			 [game]  ï¬Œ Toggle game mode
 
[show]                      ï¬Œ Useful GUI util

			 [binds]  ï¬Œ [*] Show keybind hints
  			                  ğŸ’¡ Click to execute

						[-j] ï¬Œ   Show the JSON format
						[-p] ï¬Œ   Show the pretty format
						[-d] ï¬Œ   Add custom delimiter symbol (default '>')
						[-f] ï¬Œ   Add custom file
						[-y] ï¬Œ   Custom width
						[-h] ï¬Œ   Display this help message

			 [emoji]  ï¬Œ Emoji selector

			 [pastebin]  ï¬Œ [*] Pastebin manager 
  			                  ğŸ’¡ pass [only once] '--ignore=initialclass' to disable autopaste

						[c] ï¬Œ  cliphist list and copy selected
						[d] ï¬Œ  cliphist list and delete selected
						[w] ï¬Œ  cliphist wipe database

			 [glyph]  ï¬Œ Glyph selector

			 [bookmarks]  ï¬Œ [*] Bookmark selector
  			                 ğŸ’¡ append 'bookmark_file=("/path/to/bookmarks.lst")' line inside '/home/khing/.config/hyde/hyde.conf'

						[--rebuild] ï¬Œ    force rebuild cached bookmark paths
						[--no-custom] ï¬Œ     run without custom '.lst' bookmark files

			 [screencap]  ï¬Œ Use rofi to select screenshot options 
  			                  !! kills another rofi session
 
[run]                       ï¬Œ Executable utilities

			 [audio_idle]  ï¬Œ Inhibits idle when player status: 'Playing

			 [events]  ï¬Œ Watches hyprland events and executes actions

			 [screencap]  ï¬Œ [*] Screenshot and screenrecord tool

						[--print-all] ï¬Œ   Print all outputs
						[--record-focus] ï¬Œ   Record focused monitor
						[--print-snip] ï¬Œ   Drag to manually snip an area
						[--record-snip] ï¬Œ   Drag to manually snip an area to screen record it
						[-freeze] ï¬Œ   Frozen screen, drag to manually snip an area
						[--print-monitor] ï¬Œ   Print focused monitor
						[--scan] ï¬Œ   Use 'tesseract' to scan image then add to clipboard
						[--stop] ï¬Œ   Stop every instance of Screencap
						[--reset] ï¬Œ   Reinitialize screencap
 
[inject]                    ï¬Œ User/Device specific scripts that might be useful

			 [asus_patch]  ï¬Œ Fixes issues for asus devices

			 [chaotic_aur]  ï¬Œ [*] Add chaotic aur to you mirror

						[--install] ï¬Œ  Setup Choatic Aur, append [fresh] to run in fresh install mode
						[--uninstall] ï¬Œ  Removes Chaotic Aur
						[--revert] ï¬Œ  Converts chaotic aur packages to AUR

			 [flatpak]  ï¬Œ Flatpak setup for HyDE
 
[reload]                    ï¬Œ Just reload
====================================================================================================================================

Descriptions with [*] can be expanded to show more information. Append [--help]




